 architecture improves the energy consumption and performance of\nthe 3D CMP on average about 61.33 and 9 percent respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Dec 2019 16:00:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-16"}
