how that the proposed model works effectively in managing\nthe uncertainty in solar PV and load and can provide a flexible dispatch in\nboth grid-connected and islanded modes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Dec 2019 16:26:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-16"}
