lts show that RCG\nachieves near-optimal performance at a much lower complexity compared with the\noptimal solution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Dec 2019 23:16:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 19 Apr 2020 19:08:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-21"}
