ravitational wave\nobservations with aLIGO at design sensitivity by 2026 will be even more\nstringent, becoming stronger than constraints achievable with future ATHENA\nX-ray observations before it flies in 2034.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Dec 2019 23:00:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 May 2020 20:37:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-14"}
