r frequency MHD waves to heat the plasma. The radial\ndecreases of the Poynting flux and solar wind speed inside switchbacks are due\nto a geometrical effect.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Dec 2019 18:32:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-20"}
